Sneaker.name: OVO x Air Jordan 10
Sneaker.descrption: if you're thinking it your probably right these are not walkable, but hella cool to look! The pair  of solid gold sneakers weighs over 100 pounds according to Drake, and features every little detail that the original does.

Sneaker.name: adidas x Gucci Gazelle
Sneaker.description: Gazelle but make it Gucci!  The structure is the orginal gazelle format but with gucci's unique colorways .These would be great for a polo match or a calm boat ride or even a walk in centeral park during the fall

Sneaker.name: Air Jordan 1 OG High Chicago 1985
Sneaker.description: It's nothing like the classsic jumpman ,Conceptualized by Peter Moore, the Air Jordan 1 High 'Chicago' 1985 shoe changed the way people regarded sneakers forever. This first edition honors the Chicago Bulls team colors in a full-grain leather build complete with sleek Swooshes, Wings branding and a molded collar.

Sneaker.name: MAISON MARGIELA X REEBOK'S TABI INSTAPUMP ANKLE BOOTS
Sneaker.description: What are those ! Featuring the French label’s iconic Tabi toe, the sneaker-boot hybrid comes in four colorways: “Black/Yellow,” “Black/Blue,” “Black” and “White.” The upper is constructed out of textile and leather fabric, while the chunky, sculptured sole is made from quality rubber material. Additionally, the ankle-high, slip-on pair comes with two utilitarian pull tabs, an elastic band and a four-inch heel. Rounding out the item is the sportswear brand’s signature Pump system, the Hexalite midsole and Graphlite arch bridge that provides flexibility and lightweight support.

Sneaker.name: A Bathing Ape Bapesta Kanye West College Dropout
Sneaker.description: “Patent leather BAPEs, Closet like planet of the BAPE”! This limited edition Bapesta is known as the “College Dropout” edition and was inspired by Kanye’s album of the same title. They feature a brown and tan upper with the “Dropout Bear” on the heels and red accents.

Sneaker.name: Vans x Supreme Authentic Pro “Supreme Checkered Red” low-top sneakers
Sneaker.description: Got my Vans on cuz they look like sneakers! Red/white cotton x Supreme Authentic Pro “Supreme Checkered Red” low-top sneakers from VANS featuring all-over logo print, checkerboard print, raised logo detail, round toe, front lace-up fastening, rubber sole and Waffle outsole.

Sneaker.name: Olivia Kim x Wmns Air Jordan 4 Retro 'No Cover'
Sneaker.description: Black cat, nine lives! Kim has taken the classic 'Black Cat' edition of the silhouette and put her own spin on the all-black design. Pony hair covers the vast majority of the upper, giving the design an aesthetic that nods to its source of inspiration even better than that of the OG.
